\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s76\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s76\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch After many days I discovered this great paradox: Those who bore failure in their hearts were able to illuminate the final victory, while those who felt triumphant were left by the wayside like vegetation whose life is muted and diffuse. After many days, coming from the darkest of darkness, I arrived at the light, guided not by teachings but by meditation.}{\s76\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\sa80\s103\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s103\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Thus, I told myself on the first day:}{\s103\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 1.\tab There is no meaning in life if everything ends with death.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 2.\tab All justification for actions, whether these actions are despicable or admirable, is always a new dream that leaves only emptiness ahead.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 3.\tab God is something uncertain.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 4.\tab Faith is something as variable as reason and dreams.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 5.\tab \uc1\u8220\'93What one should do\uc1\u8221\'94 may be thoroughly discussed, but in the end there is nothing that definitively supports any position.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 6.\tab The \uc1\u8220\'93responsibility\uc1\u8221\'94 of those who commit themselves to something is no greater than the responsibility of those who do not.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 7.\tab I move according to my interests, and this makes me neither a coward nor a hero.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 8.\tab \uc1\u8220\'93My interests\uc1\u8221\'94 neither justify nor discredit anything.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 9.\tab \uc1\u8220\'93My reasons\uc1\u8221\'94 are no better than the reasons of others, nor are they worse.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 10.\tab Cruelty horrifies me, but neither because of this nor in itself is it better or worse than kindness.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 11.\tab What I or others say today is of no value tomorrow.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 12.\tab To die is not better than to live or never to have been born, but neither is it worse.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 13.\tab I discovered, not through teachings but through experience and meditation, that there is no meaning in life if everything ends with death.}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381171}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381345}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
