\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 1.\tab If you have experienced the passage of the Force, you will be able to understand how, based on similar experiences but without understanding, various peoples went on to develop rites and cults that later multiplied endlessly. Through experiences like those previously described there were some who felt that their bodies had \uc1\u8220\'93doubled,\uc1\u8221\'94 and the experience of the Force gave them the sensation that they could project this energy outside themselves.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 2.\tab The Force could be \uc1\u8220\'93projected\uc1\u8221\'94 to others and also to objects particularly \uc1\u8220\'93suited\uc1\u8221\'94 to receive and conserve it. I trust it will not be difficult for you to understand the function filled by the sacraments of various religions, as well as the significance of those sacred places and priests supposedly \uc1\u8220\'93charged\uc1\u8221\'94 with the Force. When certain objects were surrounded with ceremonies and rites and worshipped with faith in temples, surely they \uc1\u8220\'93gave back\uc1\u8221\'94 to the believers the energy accumulated through repeated prayer. Since fundamental internal experience is essential to understanding in these matters, attempts at understanding based, as is normally the case, solely on externals, reveal a limitation in our knowledge of human realities\uc1\u8212\'97no matter that these externals are culture, geography, history, or tradition. }{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 3.\tab \uc1\u8220\'93Projecting,\uc1\u8221\'94 \uc1\u8220\'93charging,\uc1\u8221\'94 and \uc1\u8220\'93replenishing\uc1\u8221\'94 the Force are subjects to which we will return later. For now let me say that this same mechanism continues to operate even in secular societies where leaders and others imbued with prestige are surrounded by a special kind of aura in the eyes of those who would like to \uc1\u8220\'93touch\uc1\u8221\'94 them, acquire a scrap of their clothing, a fragment of their possessions, or even just to see them.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 4.\tab This occurs because all representations of the \uc1\u8220\'93heights\uc1\u8221\'94 extend from eye level upward, above the normal line of sight. And the \uc1\u8220\'93higher-ups\uc1\u8221\'94 are those who \uc1\u8220\'93possess\uc1\u8221\'94 kindness, wisdom, and strength. There, in the \uc1\u8220\'93heights\uc1\u8221\'94 above, we also find the hierarchies, the powers that be, and the flags of State. And we, ordinary mortals, must at all costs \uc1\u8220\'93ascend\uc1\u8221\'94 the social ladder in order to draw closer to power. What a sorry state we are in, still governed by these mechanisms, which coincide with our internal representation in which our heads are in the \uc1\u8220\'93heights\uc1\u8221\'94 and our feet stuck on the ground. What an unhappy state we are in, when we believe in these things, and believe in them because they have their own \uc1\u8220\'93reality\uc1\u8221\'94 in our internal representation. What a sorry state we are in, when our }{\s53\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}external look}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0} is nothing but an unacknowledged projection of the internal.}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381184}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381358}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
