\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s103\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s103\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Earlier I explained to you: \uc1\u8220\'93Whenever you find great strength, joy, and kindness in your heart, or when you feel free and without contradictions, immediately be internally thankful.\uc1\u8221\'94 }{\s103\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 1.\tab \uc1\u8220\'93To be thankful\uc1\u8221\'94 means to concentrate these positive moods and associate them with an image, with a representation. If you have previously linked positive states in this way, you can, upon finding yourself in a difficult situation, evoke that representation, and along with it will arise the positive quality that accompanied it earlier. Furthermore, since this mental \uc1\u8220\'93charge\uc1\u8221\'94 has been increased through previous repetitions, it is capable of displacing the negative emotions that certain situations impose.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 2.\tab Thus, whatever you ask for will return from within you amplified in benefit\uc1\u8212\'97as long as you have accumulated within yourself numerous positive states. By now it should be unnecessary to repeat that this mechanism has long been used (though in confused ways) to \uc1\u8220\'93charge\uc1\u8221\'94 external objects or persons or to externalize internal entities, believing that they would respond to prayers and supplication.}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381186}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381360}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
