\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s76\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s76\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch You must now gain sufficient insight into the various internal states you may find yourself in throughout the course of your life, and particularly in the course of your evolutionary work. I have no way to describe these states except by using images, in this case allegorical ones. These seem to me to have the virtue of \uc1\u8220\'93visually\uc1\u8221\'94 concentrating complex states and moods. The unusual approach of linking these states to one another as if they were distinct moments in a single process introduces a departure from the typically fragmented descriptions we have become accustomed to from those who normally deal with such things.}{\s76\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
