\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\itap0{\*\bkmkstart _Toc35011421}{\*\bkmkend _Toc31381191}{\f0\fs34\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch III. The External Landscape}{\*\bkmkend _Toc31381365}{\*\bkmkend _Toc35011421}{\f0\fs34\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Look at this couple slowly walking. While his arm gently encircles her waist, she rests her head softly on his welcoming shoulder. They stroll on while the autumn of leaves that fall around them is crackling and dying in yellows, reds, and violets. Young and beautiful, they continue, inevitably, into the gray overcast afternoon. A cold drizzle begins to fall on the children\uc1\u8217\'92s toys, abandoned in deserted gardens. }{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 1.\tab For some this scene revives a gentle and perhaps pleasant nostalgia. For others it awakens dreams, and for still others, promises to be fulfilled in radiant days to come. Before the same sea one person becomes anguished, while another, inspired, feels exhilarated. And a thousand more are overawed in contemplation of those frozen crags, while still others gaze in admiration at those crystals carved on such gigantic scale. Some are depressed, others uplifted before the same landscape. }{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 2.\tab A single landscape, then, may be very different for two people, but wherein does the difference lie?}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 3.\tab The same occurs with what we see or hear. Consider, for example, the word \uc1\u8220\'93future.\uc1\u8221\'94 It sets one person on edge, while another remains indifferent, and still others would sacrifice their \uc1\u8220\'93today\uc1\u8221\'94 for it.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 4.\tab Consider for example, music, or words with social or religious significance.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 5.\tab There are moments when a multitude or an entire nation will condemn or embrace a certain landscape. But does that rejection or acceptance lie in the landscape or in the hearts of that multitude or nation?}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab }{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}6.\tab Between doubt and hope, your life is oriented toward landscapes that coincide with something that is within you.}{\s53\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 7.\tab This entire world, which you have not chosen but which has been given for you to humanize, is the landscape that most grows as life grows. Therefore may your heart never say, \uc1\u8220\'93Neither the autumn, nor the sea, nor the ice-covered crag have anything to do with me.\uc1\u8221\'94 Instead may it affirm, \uc1\u8220\'93I love the reality that I build!\uc1\u8221\'94}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381192}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381366}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
