\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\itap0{\*\bkmkstart _Toc35011426}{\*\bkmkend _Toc31381196}{\f0\fs34\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch VIII. The Rider and His Shadow}{\*\bkmkend _Toc31381370}{\*\bkmkend _Toc35011426}{\f0\fs34\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch As the sun tinted the path red and the shadow of the rider lengthened along the rocks and thick underbrush, he slowed his pace until at last he stopped by a newly lit fire. An old man, rubbing his hands at the flames, greeted him. The rider dismounted and they spoke together for a time. Then the rider continued on his way. }{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch When the shadow of the rider shortened and fell beneath the horse\uc1\u8217\'92s hooves, he halted for a moment to speak with a man who hailed him from the side of the road.}{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch The rider did not slow his pace as the shadow grew long behind him, and a young man who wanted to stop him was only able to shout, \uc1\u8220\'93You\uc1\u8217\'92re going the wrong way!\uc1\u8221\'94}{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\sa80\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Finally, nightfall caused the rider to dismount, and he saw the shadow only in his soul. Then, sighing to himself and to the stars, he said:}{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \uc1\u8220\'93On a single day an old man spoke to me of loneliness, sickness, and death. A middle-aged man spoke to me of the way things are and the realities of life. And finally, I came upon a youth who did not even speak to me but only shouted out, trying to alter my course to an unknown direction. }{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \uc1\u8220\'93The old man feared losing his things and his life. The middle-aged man feared he would not be able to gain what he believed were his things and his life. The youth feared being unable to escape from his things and his life.}{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \uc1\u8220\'93Strange encounters these, where the old man suffers for his short future, seeking refuge in his long past; the middle-aged man suffers for his present situation, seeking refuge in what has happened or what will happen, depending on whether he grasps before or behind him; and the youth suffers because his short past nips at his heels, spurring on his flight toward a long future.}{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \uc1\u8220\'93And yet I recognize my own face in the faces of all three, and it seems to me that all human beings, whatever their age, can move through these times and see in them phantoms that do not exist. Or does that offense of my youth still exist today? Does my coming old age exist today? Does my death already dwell here today in this darkness? }{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \uc1\u8220\'93All suffering steals in through memory, imagination, or perception. But it is thanks to these same three pathways that thoughts, affections, and human deeds exist. So it is that even while these pathways are necessary for life, if suffering contaminates them they also become channels of destruction.}{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \uc1\u8220\'93Yet is not suffering the warning that life gives us when its flow is inverted?}{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \uc1\u8220\'93Life can be inverted by something that is done with it, perhaps unwittingly. And so it is that the old man, the middle-aged man, and the youth must have done something with their lives for them to have become \uc1\u8216\'91inverted.\uc1\u8217\'92\uc1\u8221\'94 }{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Then the rider, meditating in the darkness of the night, fell asleep. And upon sleeping he dreamt, and in his dreams the landscape became illuminated. }{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch He found himself in the center of a triangular space walled with mirrors. The mirrors reflected his image, multiplying it. Choosing one direction he saw himself as an old man. Choosing another his face was that of a middle-aged man, and in a third that of a youth. But in the center of himself, he felt like a child.}{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch Then everything began to grow dark, and when he could distinguish nothing but a heavy darkness, he awoke. }{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi274\ri274\s105\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tx0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx9360\tx10080\tx10800{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch On opening his eyes he saw the light of the sun. Then he mounted his horse, and seeing his shadow growing longer, he said to himself, \uc1\u8220\'93Contradiction inverts life and generates suffering\uc1\u8230\'85 The sun hides itself so that day becomes night, but the day will be according to what I do with it.\uc1\u8221\'94 }{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381197}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381371}{\s105\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
