\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\itap0{\*\bkmkstart _Toc35011430}{\*\bkmkend _Toc31381200}{\f0\fs34\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch XII. Compensation, Reflection, and the Future}{\*\bkmkend _Toc31381374}{\*\bkmkend _Toc35011430}{\f0\fs34\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 1.\tab Hunger dreams of satiety, the imprisoned yearn for freedom, pain longs for pleasure, and pleasure wearies of itself. Could it be that life is nothing more than action and reaction?}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 2.\tab If life is but pursuit of security for those who fear the future, self-affirmation for the disoriented, the desire for revenge for those frustrated with the past\uc1\u8212\'97what liberty, what responsibility, what commitment can be held aloft as an unvanquished banner?}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 3.\tab And if life is but a mirror that reflects a landscape, how will it ever change that which it reflects?}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 4.\tab Between the cold mechanics of pendulums and the phantasmal optics of mirrors, what do you affirm that you can affirm without denying? What do you affirm without regressing or with more than arithmetic repetition? }{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 5.\tab If you affirm that which searches for itself and whose nature is to transform itself, that which is never complete in itself and whose essence opens to the future, then you love the reality you build. This, then, is your life: the reality that you build!}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 6.\tab And there will be action and reaction, as there will be reflection and accident. But if you have opened the future, there will be nothing that can detain you. }{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 7.\tab May life speak through your mouth, and may it say, \uc1\u8220\'93There is nothing that can detain me!\uc1\u8221\'94 }{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 8.\tab Oh useless and wicked prophecy that proclaims the end of the world. I affirm that the human being shall not only continue to live but shall grow without limit. And I say, moreover, that the deniers of life wish to steal all hope\uc1\u8212\'97that beating heart of human action.}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-547\li273\ri274\s53\sl280\slmult0\itap0\tqdec\tx80\tx260\tx875\tx1595\tx2315\tx3035\tx3755\tx4475\tx5195\tx5915\tx6635\tx7355\tx8075\tx8358{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab 9.\tab In the darkest moments, may your future joy remind you of these words: \uc1\u8220\'93Life searches for growth, not for}{\s53\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0} }{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}the compensation of nothingness!\uc1\u8221\'94}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381201}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc31381375}{\s53\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
