\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-936\li229\ri-431\s37\sl240\slmult1\itap0\tqdec\tx0\tx180{\s37\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab VI.\tab }{\s37\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Sleep and Awakening}{\s37\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\uc1\u8212\'97Distinguishes between various levels of consciousness\uc1\u8212\'97sleep, semi-sleep, vigil with reverie, and full vigil\uc1\u8212\'97and their relationship to the perception of reality. External and internal senses as well as memory. }{\s37\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-936\li229\ri-431\s37\sl240\slmult1\itap0\tqdec\tx0\tx180{\s37\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab VII.\tab }{\s37\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Presence of the Force}{\s37\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\uc1\u8212\'97The growth of comprehension in vigil. The energy or Force that is rooted in and moves through the body. }{\s37\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
\pard\plain\ltrpar\ql\fi-936\li229\ri-431\s37\sl240\slmult1\itap0\tqdec\tx0\tx180{\s37\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\abinodiroverride\ltrch \tab VIII.\tab }{\s37\f0\fs22\i\lang1033{\*\listtag0}Control of the Force}{\s37\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\uc1\u8212\'97Relates the depth or superficiality of the energy to the levels of consciousness. }{\s37\f0\fs22\lang1033{\*\listtag0}\par}
